---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Patient Information | Franconia Family Dental"
  description="Everything you need to know before your visit to Franconia Family Dental — new patient info, insurance, office hours, and downloadable forms."
>
  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section
    aria-labelledby="hero-heading"
    class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-600 to-sky-700 text-white py-16 md:py-24"
  >
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 id="hero-heading" class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
        Patient Information
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-sky-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        We want your visit to be as smooth and comfortable as possible. Here you'll find everything
        you need to know before your appointment, from what to bring to payment options and office hours.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- New Patients Section -->
  <section
    aria-labelledby="new-patients-heading"
    class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white"
  >
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 id="new-patients-heading" class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">
          New Patients
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Welcome to our dental family! Here's what you can expect on your first visit.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <!-- What to Expect -->
        <div class="bg-sky-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sky-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800">What to Expect</h3>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-5 h-5 text-sky-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Warm welcome</strong> from our friendly front desk team</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-5 h-5 text-sky-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Comprehensive exam</strong> including digital X-rays and oral cancer screening</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-5 h-5 text-sky-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Personalized consultation</strong> with your dentist to discuss your oral health</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-5 h-5 text-sky-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Custom treatment plan</strong> tailored to your needs and goals</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-5 h-5 text-sky-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Professional cleaning</strong> (if time permits and clinically appropriate)</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-slate-600">
            Please arrive 15 minutes early to complete any remaining paperwork.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- What to Bring -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800">What to Bring</h3>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-sky-100 text-sky-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">1</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-slate-800">Valid Photo ID</strong>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Driver's license, state ID, or passport</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-sky-100 text-sky-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">2</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-slate-800">Insurance Card</strong>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Both front and back if applicable</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-sky-100 text-sky-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">3</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-slate-800">Completed Patient Forms</strong>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Download below or complete in office</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-sky-100 text-sky-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">4</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-slate-800">List of Medications</strong>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Including dosages and any allergies</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-sky-100 text-sky-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">5</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-slate-800">Previous Dental Records</strong>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">X-rays or records from your previous dentist (if available)</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Insurance & Payment Section -->
  <section
    id="insurance"
    aria-labelledby="insurance-heading"
    class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-slate-50"
  >
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 id="insurance-heading" class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">
          Insurance & Payment
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          We accept most major insurance plans and offer flexible payment options to make dental care accessible.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Accepted Insurance -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sky-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-6 h-6 text-sky-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800">Accepted Insurance</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
            We work with most major dental insurance providers. If you don't see your plan listed, please contact us to verify coverage.
          </p>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-4 h-4 text-sky-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              Delta Dental
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-4 h-4 text-sky-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              MetLife
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-4 h-4 text-sky-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              Cigna
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-4 h-4 text-sky-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              Aetna
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-4 h-4 text-sky-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              Guardian
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-4 h-4 text-sky-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              United Healthcare
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-4 h-4 text-sky-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              Blue Cross
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-4 h-4 text-sky-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              And more...
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Payment Options -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sky-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-6 h-6 text-sky-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 10h18M7 15h1m4 0h1m-7 4h12a3 3 0 003-3V8a3 3 0 00-3-3H6a3 3 0 00-3 3v8a3 3 0 003 3z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800">Payment Options</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
            We believe everyone deserves quality dental care. We offer multiple payment options for your convenience.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 9V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2m2 4h10a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm7-5a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-slate-800">Cash & Check</strong>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Personal checks and cash accepted</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 10h18M7 15h1m4 0h1m-7 4h12a3 3 0 003-3V8a3 3 0 00-3-3H6a3 3 0 00-3 3v8a3 3 0 003 3z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-slate-800">Credit & Debit Cards</strong>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Visa, Mastercard, American Express, Discover</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-slate-800">Flexible Financing</strong>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">CareCredit and in-house payment plans available</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Office Hours Section -->
  <section
    aria-labelledby="hours-heading"
    class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white"
  >
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 id="hours-heading" class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">
          Office Hours
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          We offer convenient hours to fit your busy schedule, including early morning and Saturday appointments.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-sky-50 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
          <table class="w-full">
            <caption class="sr-only">Weekly office hours schedule</caption>
            <thead>
              <tr class="bg-sky-600 text-white">
                <th scope="col" class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-semibold">Day</th>
                <th scope="col" class="px-6 py-4 text-right font-semibold">Hours</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-sky-100">
              <tr class="bg-white hover:bg-sky-50 transition-colors">
                <th scope="row" class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-medium text-slate-800">Monday</th>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-right text-slate-600">8:00 AM – 5:00 PM</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-sky-50/50 hover:bg-sky-50 transition-colors">
                <th scope="row" class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-medium text-slate-800">Tuesday</th>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-right text-slate-600">8:00 AM – 5:00 PM</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-white hover:bg-sky-50 transition-colors">
                <th scope="row" class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-medium text-slate-800">Wednesday</th>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-right text-slate-600">8:00 AM – 5:00 PM</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-sky-50/50 hover:bg-sky-50 transition-colors">
                <th scope="row" class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-medium text-slate-800">Thursday</th>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-right text-slate-600">8:00 AM – 5:00 PM</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-white hover:bg-sky-50 transition-colors">
                <th scope="row" class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-medium text-slate-800">Friday</th>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-right text-slate-600">8:00 AM – 3:00 PM</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-sky-50/50 hover:bg-sky-50 transition-colors">
                <th scope="row" class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-medium text-slate-800">Saturday</th>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-right text-slate-600">
                  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                    9:00 AM – 1:00 PM
                    <span class="text-xs bg-sky-200 text-sky-800 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-medium">Limited</span>
                  </span>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-white">
                <th scope="row" class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-medium text-slate-800">Sunday</th>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-right text-slate-500 italic">Closed</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-xl">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
            </svg>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-amber-800">Dental Emergencies</strong>
              <p class="text-amber-700 text-sm mt-1">
                For after-hours dental emergencies, please call our main line. Our answering service will connect you with the on-call dentist.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Patient Forms Section -->
  <section
    aria-labelledby="forms-heading"
    class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-slate-50"
  >
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 id="forms-heading" class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">
          Patient Forms
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Save time at your appointment by downloading and completing these forms in advance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <ul role="list" class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <li>
          <!-- FIX: changed href from #new-patient-form to #forms-heading (no broken anchor) -->
          <a
            href="#forms-heading"
            class="group flex flex-col bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:border-sky-300 hover:shadow-md transition-all focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-sky-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 h-full"
          >
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-sky-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-sky-200 transition-colors">
              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-7 h-7 text-sky-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2 group-hover:text-sky-700 transition-colors">
              New Patient Form
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-4 flex-1">
